oard contains a "Dimensional Progress" section with all 5 dimension names (`structural`, `ruleCoherence`, `integration`, `outputQuality`, `systemFitness`) and their scores displayed in the table. | If no &quot;Dimensional Progress&quot; section appears: check whether the renderer detects the presence of `dimensions` arrays in scored JSONL records<br>If some dimensions are missing from the table: verify all five dimension names (`structural`, `ruleCoherence`, `integration`, `outputQuality`, `systemFitness`) are recognized by the reducer<br>If no output files are created: confirm `reduce-state.cjs` received the correct positional argument (runtime root path, not `--input`/`--output` flags) |
